---
title: Teriyaki Chicken & Garlic Rice Bowl with Japanese Mayo
description: When mayo gets together with Japanese dressing, our tastebuds start doing a happy dance. And when juicy pieces of teriyaki chicken, crunchy broccolini and mouth-watering garlic rice join the mix, it's our kind of party!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/teriyaki-chicken-garlic-rice-bowl-935912b6.jpg
